sections.comments: This section of HIST 333A is restricted to Honours students who want to attend term 1 only.  Students who want to attend the full version of HIST 333 should register in HIST 333C 001.HIST 333A:  Any student who foresees difficulty attending this course synchronously, because of issues such as a lack of access to high speed internet or being too far outside our time zone, should contact the instructor as soon as possible.
